-- 2010-11-10T10:31:38Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-10/tod-s-chief-executive-della-valle-says-fashion-company-growing-very-well-.html
Tod’s SpA Chief Executive Officer
Diego Della Valle said the company’s business is doing “very
well.” He declined to give figures ahead of the company’s
earnings report tomorrow, except to say that he will be “a very
happy man.”  Della Valle spoke at a conference in London.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Celeste Perri at 
 cperri@bloomberg.net  